'''三氧化二锰'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为Mn<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>，其中锰处于+3氧化态。<ref>Catherine E. Housecroft, Alan G. Sharpe. Inorganic Chemistry (Second Edition). Pearson Education Limited, 2005. pp 614-615. Manganese(III). ISBN 0130-39913-2</ref>

== 制备 ==
在800℃以下将[[二氧化锰|二氧化锰]]于空气中灼烧可以得到α-Mn<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>（更高温度得到Mn<sub>3</sub>O<sub>4</sub>）<ref name = "Greenwood">{{Greenwood&Earnshaw}}</ref>，在600-800℃空气中加热Mn<sup>2+</sup>的[[硝酸盐|硝酸盐]]、[[草酸盐|草酸盐]]或[[碳酸盐|碳酸盐]]也能得到α-Mn<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub><ref name = "wj">谢高阳 等. 无机化学丛书 第九卷 锰分族 铁系 铂系. 科学出版社, 2012.3. pp 31</ref>。γ-Mn<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>由[[氢氧化锰|氢氧化锰]](II)的脱水氧化制得。<ref name = "Greenwood"/> 很多制备纳米晶体Mn<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>的方法已有报道，如通过氧化Mn<sup>2+</sup>盐或还原MnO<sub>2</sub>制备。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Preparation of α-Mn<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub> and MnO from thermal decomposition of MnCO<sub>3</sub> and control of morphology|author=Shuijin Lei, Kaibin Tang, Zhen Fang, Qiangchun Liu, Huagui Zheng|journal=Materials Letters|volume=60|year=2006|page=53|doi=10.1016/j.matlet.2005.07.0}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Yuan|first1=Zhong-Yong|last2=Ren|first2=Tie-Zhen|last3=Du|first3=Gaohui|last4=Su|first4=Bao-Lian|title=A facile preparation of single-crystalline α-Mn<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub> nanorods by ammonia-hydrothermal treatment of MnO2|journal=Chemical Physics Letters|volume=389|issue=1-3|year=2004|pages=83–86|issn=00092614|doi=10.1016/j.cplett.2004.03.064}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Chandra|first1=Navin|last2=Bhasin|first2=Sanjeev|last3=Sharma|first3=Meenakshi|last4=Pal|first4=Deepti|title=A room temperature process for making Mn<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub> nano-particles and γ-MnOOH nano-rods|journal=Materials Letters|volume=61|issue=17|year=2007|pages=3728–3732|issn=0167577X|doi=10.1016/j.matlet.2006.12.024}}</ref>

需要注意的是，Mn<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>和MnOOH并不是相同的，MnOOH在空气中加热，会在约300 °C时产生MnO<sub>2</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Kohler|first1=Thomas|last2=Armbruster|first2=Thomas|last3=Libowitzky|first3=Eugen|title=Hydrogen Bonding and Jahn–Teller Distortion in Groutite,α-MnOOH, and Manganite,γ-MnOOH, and Their Relations to the Manganese Dioxides Ramsdellite and Pyrolusite|journal=Journal of Solid State Chemistry|volume=133|issue=2|year=1997|pages=486–500|issn=00224596|doi=10.1006/jssc.1997.7516}}</ref>

== 结构及物理性质 ==
三氧化二锰和其它过渡金属氧化物不同，并不采取[[刚玉|刚玉]]（Al<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>）的结构<ref name = "Greenwood" />。已知它有常见的α型和γ型<ref name = "Wells">Wells A.F. (1984) ''Structural Inorganic Chemistry'' 5th edition Oxford Science Publications ISBN 0-19-855370-6</ref>，和在高压下有着CaIrO<sub>3</sub>结构的晶型。<ref>High Pressure Phase transition in Mn<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub> to the CaIrO<sub>3</sub>-type Phase Santillan, J.; Shim, S. American Geophysical Union, Fall Meeting 2005, abstract #MR23B-0050</ref>α-Mn<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>是黑色固体，为斜方晶系，[[晶格常数|晶格常数]]a=941.2 pm、b=941 pm、c=942.3 pm，[[奈耳温度|奈耳温度]]约为80K。<ref name="wj" />γ-Mn<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>则是立方密排结构，奈耳温度为39K。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Ferrimagnetism in γ-Manganese Sesquioxide (γ−Mn<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>) Nanoparticles|author=Kim S. H, Choi B. J,Lee G.H., Oh S. J., Kim B., Choi H. C., Park J, Chang Y.|journal=Journal of the Korean Physical Society|volume=46|issue=4|year=2005|page=941}}</ref>

== 化学性质 ==
三氧化二锰是一种氧化剂，可以将[[盐酸|盐酸]]氧化为[[氯气|氯气]]：<ref name=fml>曹忠良, 王珍云. 无机化学反应方程式手册. 湖南科学技术出版社, 1985.9. pp.302 【Mn<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>】</ref>
: Mn<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub> + 6 HCl（稀） —<u><sup>Δ</sup></u>→ 2 MnCl<sub>2</sub> + Cl<sub>2</sub>↑ + 3 H<sub>2</sub>O
和浓[[硫酸|硫酸]]反应，则放出[[氧气|氧气]]：<ref name=fml />
: 2 Mn<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub> + H<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub>（浓） —<u><sup>Δ</sup></u>→ 4 MnSO<sub>4</sub> + O<sub>2</sub>↑ + 4 H<sub>2</sub>O

三氧化二锰也能氧化有机物，如在硫酸的水溶液中将4-氟甲苯氧化为4-氟苯甲醛，<ref name=ZhangQM>张启蒙, 薛叙明, 马金花, 李玉辉, 马伟刚. [http://www.cnki.com.cn/Article/CJFDTOTAL-HNHG201003019.htm 三氧化二锰氧化法合成对氟苯甲醛的绿色工艺] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cnki.com.cn/Article/CJFDTOTAL-HNHG201003019.htm |date=20190711154701 }}. 精细化工中间体, 2010, 40(3):47-49.</ref>将4,4'-二甲基-2,2'-联吡啶氧化为2,2'-联吡啶-4,4'-二甲醛，<ref>Wang, Yong; Zhang, Lipan; Guo, Liangqi; Wu, Ji; Wang, Fayun; Guo, Yanchun. Process for preparation of <nowiki>[2,​2'-​bipyridine]​</nowiki>-​4,​4'-​dicarboxaldehyde [P]. 2011. CN 102295596 A</ref>以及将4-甲基苯磺酸氧化为4-甲酰基苯磺酸。<ref>严新, 宋萌, 林周, 王遵尧. [http://www.cnki.com.cn/Article/CJFDTOTAL-JSHG200404010.htm 用Mn<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>氧化法合成对羰基苯磺酸] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cnki.com.cn/Article/CJFDTOTAL-JSHG200404010.htm |date=20190712084337 }}. 江苏化工, 2004, 32(4):31-33.</ref>

三氧化二锰和氧化镧在高温反应，可以得到正交晶系的LaMnO<sub>3</sub>，这种化合物与GdFeO<sub>3</sub>异构。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=van Roosmalen|first1=J.A.M.|last2=van Vlaanderen|first2=P.|last3=Cordfunke|first3=E.H.P.|last4=IJdo|first4=W.L.|last5=IJdo|first5=D.J.W.|title=Phases in the Perovskite-Type LaMnO<sub>3+δ</sub> Solid Solution and the La<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>-Mn<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub> Phase Diagram|journal=Journal of Solid State Chemistry|volume=114|issue=2|year=1995|pages=516–523|issn=00224596|doi=10.1006/jssc.1995.1078}}</ref>它也能直接和[[六氟乙酰丙酮|六氟乙酰丙酮]]在[[环己烷|环己烷]]中回流下反应，生成三(六氟乙酰丙酮)合锰(III)。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Zhang|first1=Haitao|last2=Li|first2=Bo|last3=Dikarev|first3=Evgeny V.|title=Mn(III) Hexafluoroacetylacetonate as an Oxidative Agent in the Synthesis of Heterobimetallic β-Diketonates|journal=Journal of Cluster Science|volume=19|issue=1|year=2007|pages=311–321|issn=1040-7278|doi=10.1007/s10876-007-0174-1}}</ref>

== 应用 ==
三氧化二锰在无机上可以用作[[一氧化氮|一氧化氮]]选择性还原的催化剂<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Tang|first1=Xingfu|last2=Li|first2=Junhua|last3=Sun|first3=Liang|last4=Hao|first4=Jiming|title=Origination of N<sub>2</sub>O from NO reduction by NH<sub>3</sub> over β-MnO<sub>2</sub> and α-Mn<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>|journal=Applied Catalysis B: Environmental|volume=99|issue=1-2|year=2010|pages=156–162|issn=09263373|doi=10.1016/j.apcatb.2010.06.012}}</ref>，在有机合成中用作[[氧化剂|氧化剂]]<ref name=ZhangQM /><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Sihaib|first1=Z.|last2=Puleo|first2=F.|last3=Garcia-Vargas|first3=J.M.|last4=Retailleau|first4=L.|last5=Descorme|first5=C.|last6=Liotta|first6=L.F.|last7=Valverde|first7=J.L.|last8=Gil|first8=S.|last9=Giroir-Fendler|first9=A.|title=Manganese oxide-based catalysts for toluene oxidation|journal=Applied Catalysis B: Environmental|volume=209|year=2017|pages=689–700|issn=09263373|doi=10.1016/j.apcatb.2017.03.042}}</ref>，它也能用作钯铂合金的载体<ref>徐鹏, 吴志星, 邓积光, 刘雨溪, 谢少华, 郭广生, 戴洪兴. [http://www.cnki.com.cn/Article/CJFDTOTAL-CHUA201701014.htm 有序介孔三氧化二锰负载PdPt合金：一种高效的甲烷催化燃烧催化剂] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cnki.com.cn/Article/CJFDTOTAL-CHUA201701014.htm |date=20190711154947 }}. 催化学报, 2017, 38(1):92-105.</ref>或电极材料<ref>张杰, 许家胜. 一种三氧化二锰多孔微米片/泡沫镍复合电极材料的制备方法[P], CN105355468 A. 2016.</ref>。

